  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à libgusb</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libgusb</application> package contains the GObject
      wrappers for <application>libusb-1.0</application> that makes it
      easy to do asynchronous control, bulk et interrupt transfers with
      proper cancellation et integration into a mainloop.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

